Ext.data.JsonP['Outline_View']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Outline View</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083303\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Outline View</h1>\n    <p>This page describes what the Outline View is and how to display it.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083303_OutlineView-Introduction\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Introduction</span></h2>\n    <p>The Outline View displays a hierarchical grouping of the elements of your code, such as variables and functions. Use this view to get a high-level overview of your code. You can double-click an element in the Outline View to jump to that spot in your code.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083303_OutlineView-Instructions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Instructions</span></h2>\n    <p>Studio displays the Outline View in Web Perspective by default, and it is located in the lower left corner of the window. To open the view manually:    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox panel panel\">\n    <ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>From the <strong class=\" \">Window</strong> menu, select <strong class=\" \">Show View &gt; Outline</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>To close the <strong class=\" \">Outline View</strong>, click the Close button (<strong class=\" \">X</strong>) in the upper right of the tab.    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083303/outline_view.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083303/outline_view.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083303_OutlineView-RelatedTopics\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Related Topics</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Bookmarks_View\">Bookmarks View</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Tasks_View\">Tasks View</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083303\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Outline View"});